    <h1>Randomizer — Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: 2026-05-05</p>

    <p>Randomizer is built by BroooApps.</p>

    <h2>Data we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Anonymous usage analytics</strong> — crash reports and broad usage patterns. No personal identifiers.</li>
      <li><strong>Ad identifiers</strong> — used by Google AdMob to serve ads. You can reset or limit this in your Android settings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we never collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, email, phone number, or contacts.</li>
      <li>Your location.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>Randomizer uses Google AdMob to display ads. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google's privacy policy</a> for details on how AdMob handles data.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:swapniltiwari775@gmail.com">swapniltiwari775@gmail.com</a>.</p>
